txt.en: Many threats can be found in Seregost's courtyards and terraces.\n\nYou should defeat enemies in Seregost.

A note is pinned to the board, written by a firm hand:

'[placeholder],
I suspect you will be checking these boards frequently. Should you find another way up to Seregost, as I suspect you will, take out as many Merrevail and Uruk-hai as you can. Any you deal with now lessens the threat our larger attack force encounters later.

Fight Well,
Faeron'
Many enemies lurk in Seregost's courtyards and terraces, each a threat to the Free People.
